ull, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1003424, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 96, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Most surely the first house appointed for men is the one at Mecca, blessed and a guidance for the nations.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Be-shak sab se pehla makaan jo logo’n ke liye banaya gaya hai woh Makkah mein hai mubarak hai aur aalameen ke liye mujassam (mukammal) hidaayat hai.", "Urdu": "بےشک سب سے پہلا مکان جو لوگوں کے لئے بنایا گیا ہے وہ مکّہ میں ہے مبارک ہے اور عالمین کے لئے مجسم ہدایت ہے۔", "RArabic": "INNA AWWALA BAITINW WUDI’A LINNAASI LALLAZEE BI BAKKATA MUBAARAKANW WA HUDAL LIL ’AALAMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "اِنَّ اَوَّلَ بَيْتٍ وُّضِعَ لِلنَّاسِ لَلَّذِيْ بِبَكَّةَ مُبٰرَكًا وَّهُدًى لِّلْعٰلَمِيْنَ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1003425, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 97, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In it are clear signs, the standing place of Ibrahim, and whoever enters it shall be secure, and pilgrEnglishImage to the House is incumbent upon men for the sake of Allah, (upon) everyone who is able to undertake the journey to it; and whoever disbelieves, then surely Allah is Self-sufficient, above any need of the worlds.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Is mein khuli huwi nishaaniya, maqaam'e Ibrahim alaihis salaam hai aur jo is mein daakhil ho jaayega woh mehfooz ho jaayega aur Allah ke liye logo’n par is ghar ka hajj karna waajib hai agar is raah ki istetaat (haisiyat) rakhte ho aur jo kaafir ho jaaye to Khuda tamaam aalameen se be-neyaaz hai.", "Urdu": "اس میں کھلی ہوئی نشانیاں مقام ابراہیم ؑہے اور جو اس میں داخل ہوجائے گا وہ محفوظ ہوجائے گا اور اللہ کے لئے لوگوں پر اس گھر کا حج کرنا واجب ہے اگر اس راہ کی استطاعت رکھتے ہوں اور جو کافر ہوجائے تو خدا تمام عالمین سے بے نیاز ہے۔", "RArabic": "FEEHI AAYAATUM BAIYINAATUM MAQAAMU IBRAAHEEMA WA MAN DAKHALAHOO KAANA AAMINAA; WA LILLAAHI ’ALAN NAASI HIJJUL BAITI MANIS TATAA’A ILAIHI SABEELAA; WA MAN KAFARA FA INNAL LAAHA GHANIYYUN ’ANIL ’AALAMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "فِيْهِ اٰيٰتٌۢ بَيِّنٰتٌ مَّقَامُ اِبْرٰهِيْمَ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": "ج ", "ArabicText2": "وَمَنْ دَخَلَهٗ كَانَ اٰمِنًا", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": "ط ", "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": "وَّلِلهِ عَلَى النَّاسِ حِجُّ الْبَيْتِ مَنِ اسْتَطَاعَ اِلَيْهِ سَبِيْلًا", "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": "ط ", "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": "وَّمَنْ كَفَرَ فَاِنَّ اللهَ غَنِيٌّ عَنِ الْعٰلَمِيْنَ", "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "Ar